flowchart TD
    client["Client test caller\nsrc/backend/tests/api/test_sync_stream_contract_parity.py"] -->|POST /api/agents/run payload:{query,thread_id,user_id}\nWhy: establish sync contract baseline| syncRoute["router: src/backend/routers/agent.py::runtime_agent_run"]
    client -->|POST /api/agents/run/stream same payload\nWhy: verify completion parity| streamRoute["router: src/backend/routers/agent.py::runtime_agent_run_stream"]

    syncRoute -->|forwards RuntimeAgentRunRequest + db + tracing handle| runSvc["service: src/backend/services/agent_service.py::run_runtime_agent"]
    streamRoute -->|creates SSE StreamingResponse| streamSvc["service: src/backend/services/agent_service.py::stream_runtime_agent"]

    streamSvc -->|trigger: _get_or_compile_stream_runtime()\nData: cached runtime instance| runtimeCache["service: agent_service._get_or_compile_stream_runtime"]
    runtimeCache -->|if cache miss, compile once per process| compileFn["service: agent_service._compile_stream_runtime"]
    streamSvc -->|trigger: runtime.ainvoke(payload,...)\nWhy: final payload parity with sync response| runSvc

    runSvc -->|returns RuntimeAgentRunResponse\nData: output, sub_queries, tool_assignments,\nretrieval_results, validation_results, graph_state, thread_id, checkpoint_id| syncResult["sync HTTP JSON response"]
    runSvc -->|mapped in stream_runtime_agent to completed.data:\nagent_name, output, sub_queries, tool_assignments,\nthread_id, checkpoint_id| completedEvent["SSE event: completed"]

    syncResult -->|test assertion compares keys/semantics| parityAssert["test_runtime_agent_run_contract_stays_stable"]
    completedEvent -->|test assertion compares with syncResult values| parityAssert2["test_runtime_agent_stream_completed_payload_matches_sync_final_values"]

    decision["Tradeoff note:\nstream completed payload intentionally excludes large fields\n(graph_state/retrieval/validation) to keep SSE frames small,\nwhile preserving parity for final answer semantics needed by UI."]:::note
    streamSvc --- decision

    classDef note fill:#f8f5e6,stroke:#8a7f52,color:#222;
